      <title>澳门 11 月博彩收入增长 14.9%，超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/macau-gaming-revenue-rises-14-9-in-november-exceeds-estimate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[11 月份，澳门博彩收入增长 14.9%，超出了分析师的预期，而由于缺乏假期，11 月份的博彩收入通常较为低迷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/macau-gaming-revenue-rises-14-9-in-november-exceeds-estimate</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 05:17:13 GMT</pubDate>
